        <id>https://cluzeau.pro/event-sourcing/</id>
        
        <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Event sourcing is an approach to software development where every action that changes the state of a system is captured as an immutable event and stored in an event log. By replaying these events, the system&#x27;s state can be reconstructed at any point in time, providing a complete audit trail of all changes and enabling advanced features.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</summary>
        
